(260, 'Golden Tulip Hotel-Kumasi', 'This remarkable hotel, the Golden Tulip Kumasi City is a first class African style business hotel set in extensive tropical gardens in the central business district of the Ashanti regional capital in Kumasi. Kumasi is the capital city of the Ashanti Regio', '50561abf66a8d', '2012-09-16 18:24:25', 1),
(261, 'Lake Bosomtwe', 'One of Ghana''s popular Recreational Centers, Lake Bosomtwe is located 30km South East of Kumasi.This lake and its surrounding crater was created by a large meteorite strike that took place around 1.07 million years ago. The lake is around 25sq km, and up ', '505f8a42874eb', '2012-09-23 22:11:44', 1),
(262, 'Shai Hills', 'Shai Hills Resource Reserve is only 51 square kilometres and is the wildlife park closest to Accra. It takes less than an hour to reach the park on the road to the Volta lake. The park is famous for the large bands of olive baboon that over-run the highwa', '50695bdb48986', '2012-10-01 08:50:26', 1),
(263, 'Elmina Town', 'Elmina is a town that is the capital of Komenda/Edina/Eguafo/Abirem district, a district in the Central Region of Akanland, Ghana', '50b20670c09bd', '2012-11-25 11:43:10', 1),
(264, 'Central Market - Bantama, Kumasi', 'Kumasi, the capital of Ghanaâ€™s Ashanti region, was named the Garden City of West Africa by the then colonial head of the Gold Coast. Kumasi also happens to be the seat of the Asante monarchy, whose head is the Asantehene â€“ Otumfuo Osei Tutu II. The As', '50bbb0074ccaa', '2012-12-02 19:36:12', 1),
(265, 'Nzulezu - stilt village', 'The village of Nzulezo is located near the village of Beyin, roughly 90 kilometers west of Takoradi, in the Jomoro District of the Western Region of Ghana. Nzulezo overlooks the Lake Tadane, and is entirely made up of stilts and platforms.', '5129ec752bdf7', '2013-02-24 10:28:42', 1),
(266, 'African Choral Festival 2013', 'African Choral Festival 2013', '517163c140e32', '2013-04-19 15:01:33', 1),
(267, 'Smoothy''s Osu', 'You want something healthy and fast? Smoothyâ€™s serves a variety of dairy products and other tasty foods like Salad and Juices, they also have comfortable furniture to accommodate everyone.\r\nLocation: Opposite the Shell filling station on the Oxford Stre', '51876e71d6132', '2013-05-06 08:44:07', 1),
(268, 'Young Boxer: Gastonic Hyde', 'Young Boxer: Gastonic Hyde from James Town', '5199eb07b1c44', '2013-05-20 09:00:00', 1),
(270, 'La Cigale wedding venue', 'La Cigale is a All In One Venue, specialising in weddings, conferences, self-catering accommodation and corporate functions.\r\n\r\nThe improved wedding venue can now accommodate up to 120 guests. We offer a large variety of menus which can be tailor made ref', '519f5934121e3', '2013-05-24 11:57:07', 1),
(271, 'Judo in Ghana', 'Judo is a modern martial art, combat and Olympic sport created in Japan in 1882 by Jigoro Kano. Its most prominent feature is its competitive element, where the objective is to either throw or takedown an opponent to the ground or force an opponent to sub', '51a72d0b61aa7', '2013-05-30 10:38:28', 1),
(272, 'Mim Bour (mountain top apartment)', 'Mim is a populated town in the Brong-Ahafo region and this mountain top apartment can be found in the Desmond Plantations, not too far from the Cashew Processing Factory.', '51b1a557156c9', '2013-06-07 09:13:57', 1),
