('1238969358', 'Funeral for the Monkeys', '1238969358.jpg', '98', 'Due to this spiritual nature, economic role, health support of this monkeys. Burial and funerals are normally preformed for the death of any monkeys.In the same vein the birth and death of any community member, the monkeys are accordingly informed through the pouring of libation and other sacrifices. ', NULL, 277, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
