('1238969551', 'Access to the Monkey Sanctuary', '1238969551.jpg', '98', 'Access to the sacred grove until UNDP GEF intervention in 2005 been a taboo and a restricted place, especially for women, the opinion leaders had to lift the Spiritual Embargo to allow in the commencement of the project as well as receive Tourists both (men and woman).', NULL, 264, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1238969735', 'Monkey', '1238969735.jpg', '98', 'The eating and dancing of the monkeys towards the overseers (okomfo) house represents overall community health at a particular point in time. The continuous mid-night fighting among monkey may symbolize uncleanness among community members or an imminent out break of disease. It is among the collection of these and many other signs of the monkeys that reveal their super human native to the local community of Duasidan', NULL, 255, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1238969801', 'Monkey', '1238969801.jpg', '98', 'There had had in historical times a festival in honor of the monkeys. This has however, died down due to modernity in religion and the death of the key people who had interest in the ritual performance of the monkey.', NULL, 286, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
