('1241070211', 'Volley Ball', '1241070211.jpg', '107', 'When you get there, get into interaction with the village folk if you want to experience authentic Ghanaian hospitality. There is nothing like playing around the beach with the village children who are always around. ', NULL, 293, '2009-04-30 05:34:46', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1241070307', 'Bojo Beach', '1241070307.jpg', '107', 'The beach area is another kind of island situated between the canal and the sea right on a stretch of sand bar. The sand bar has so much to offer that will surprise you. To get to the sand bar, you will have to cruise either by the Bojo Cruiser or a canoe over one of the Densu distributaries.', NULL, 282, '2009-04-30 05:34:46', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1241070372', 'Volley Ball', '1241070372.jpg', '107', 'The most remarkable experiences come from the cuisine, wide range of assorted and local beverages. For an eventful day, you can take to swimming, water cruising, fishing, and volleyball, sand bathing, oyster trapping and more. Afraid? Wait a minute; there are lifeguards ready to rescue you. The lovely and lively youthful employees are a delight to interact with; their infectious smiles are never to be forgotten.', NULL, 272, '2009-04-30 05:34:46', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1241070820', 'Bojo Beach ', '1241070820.jpg', '107', 'The white sand beach is very clean so it is not surprising that most patrons prefer to hang around there.To get here,drive pass MacCathy Hill and pass Weija junction, then you start looking out for the old police barrier just ahead, on your left-hand side of the barrier is the Apalku or Kokrobite junction.Keep driving and within 5 minutes, you will drive through the Apalku village, start looking out for the imposing yellow Bojo Beach sign post from here that directs you to the left, you toss onto the dusty road and within seconds you will say voila! To Bojo. There is so much car parking space and excellent security at the car park. ', NULL, 366, '2009-04-30 05:34:46', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 4, 1, 1, 0, NULL),
