('1278890773', 'Boat ride', '1278890773.jpg', '203', 'Life jackets are provided by Sajuna Beach Club, free of charge. Professional captains on the motor boat and tourist boat will take you on the Volta River for an unforgettable boat trip.', 'dcDhSGv-erg', 2189, '2010-07-11 23:26:13', 'admin', 182, 37, 1, 0, NULL),
