('1279497708', 'Accra Railway Station', '1279497708.jpg', '204', 'This is the main railway terminal in Accra. The intercity services are limited and the main route is from here to Sakumono and Nsawam. Railway services have not developed much beyond what was established during the colonial period.\nStory by AMA ASAREBEA -----------------------\nEdited by ADJOA KORANTENG------------------\nSet Programming by NANA K. ANING------------------\nPhotography by KWAKU CHINTOH', 'COMG1ZWU3Zs', 702, '2010-07-19 00:01:48', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
