('1279498247', 'Traffic', '1279498247.jpg', '204', 'I guess this picture virtually speaks for itself.  I would be stuck in this intolerable traffic jam if I had boarded a cab.  And worse would be inhaling fumes from the exhaust pipes of all these cars.  No wonder we are always getting sick.  This is just pure air pollution.  Phewwwww, thank God for the train.', NULL, 468, '2010-07-19 00:10:47', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279498363', 'Ama, enjoying her Novel', '1279498363.jpg', '204', 'This novel is so interesting that I canâ€™t put this book down, itâ€™s totally addictive.  Iâ€™m feeling so relaxed because the seats in this train is so comfortable.  Well mokocharlie fans Iâ€™m about to reach my destination.  And this is the part where I say thank you for reading my photo story.\r\nChoa!\r\n', NULL, 425, '2010-07-19 00:12:43', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279498650', 'Ama buys an ice-cream to cool down', '1279498650.jpg', '204', 'The one thing I enjoy about train rides are the stations.  At each stop you can get refreshments sold to you by hawkers.  You can get anything from ice-cream to cakes.  And as you cans see Iâ€™m getting myself some ice-cream to cool down.  Another interesting thing Iâ€™ve noticed is hawkers by the train stations donâ€™t harass you like the ones on the streets.  So I always get the opportunity to buy without any influence.', NULL, 458, '2010-07-19 00:17:30', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279498977', 'Reading', '1279498977.jpg', '204', 'Have you realized that itâ€™s virtually impossible to concentrate while reading in a noisy environment?  Well, try riding the train and you will see the difference.  You will surely have all the peace and serenity you need to enjoy a good novel', NULL, 465, '2010-07-19 00:22:57', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279499043', 'Aloneness ', '1279499043.jpg', '204', 'Most people are not used to using the train down here, so itâ€™s mostly empty.  That can only mean one thing, a lonely ride.  However if youâ€™re like me and enjoy peace and quiet then you will love the ride.  Itâ€™s a perfect time and place to recollect on a dayâ€™s work.', NULL, 484, '2010-07-19 00:24:03', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279499244', 'Stop', '1279499244.jpg', '204', 'I guess this picture virtually speaks for itself.  I would be stuck in this intolerable traffic jam if I had boarded a cab.  And worse would be inhaling fumes from the exhaust pipes of all these cars.  No wonder we are always getting sick.  This is just pure air pollution.  Phewwwww, thank God for the train.', NULL, 557, '2010-07-19 00:27:24', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279501919', 'My Photo Story 3 : Ama tells her story', '1279501919.jpg', '204', ' A lady in subtle formal pink, this can only mean one thing, Iâ€™m a working class woman.  Hi guys my name is Ama.  Life in Ghana can really be frustrating especially when you work in a reputable company like me and cannot afford to be late.  How does one avert this absurd traffic congestion?  Well I will tell you how, by using the rail form of transportation.  I donâ€™t have time to be stuck in traffic for long hours as my family totally depends on me, since I do all the cooking at home.  And thatâ€™s why I love using the train; Iâ€™m totally guaranteed to reach home on time.  Keep on reading mokocharlie fans and I will show you how I beat the traffic everydayâ€¦', 'COMG1ZWU3Zs', 887, '2010-07-19 01:11:59', 'admin', 15, 3, 1, 0, NULL);
