('1279501840', 'My Photo Story: Aloneness', '1279501840.jpg', '204', 'Most people are not used to using the train down here, so itâ€™s mostly empty.  That can only mean one thing, a lonely ride.  However if youâ€™re like me and enjoy peace and quiet then you will love the ride.  Itâ€™s a perfect time and place to recollect on a dayâ€™s work. This train runs Sakumono and Accra and this is how it''s first class looks like. It has a well designed leather seat which is very comfortable to make one enjoy the ride.', '', 790, '2010-07-19 01:10:40', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1279501226', 'My Photo Story: Ama enters the train', '1279501226.jpg', '204', 'One must be careful when climbing the steps to the train, it can be very tricky. On getting here early, one is able to find a good seat in the First class coach. The second class is usually crowded. And it''s 60pesewas for First class and 50pesewas for the second class', '', 577, '2010-07-19 01:00:26', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
