('1279501711', 'My Photo Story: Aloneness', '1279501711.jpg', '204', 'A train ride is so comfortable.  Unlike a car whereby you get tossed left and right each time the car turns.  I mean one can do some work in peace and comfort without having to worry about holding their laptops tight every second.  If you have a deadline you can be sure to complete it well before you reach work so you donâ€™t get fired.  Trains can sure be life savers!', NULL, 694, '2010-07-19 01:08:31', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
