('1291154602', 'Ave Maria Resort and Wellness Centre ', '1291154602.jpg', '224', 'Ave Maria is situated on the coast of Ghana. The Resort is in a tranquil setting overlooking the Gulf of Guinea. The Greenwich Meridian Rock lies just meters from the hotel and Pool Deck. The Centre of the Earth. Ave Maria is the gateway to places of Interest and Tourist attractions. Botanical Garden Tours, Coastal Exploration, Local Markets, Street Shopping etc. The Resort is only 30 minutes drive from Kotoke International Airport, Accra Main Line+233 22 213758 / 61 www.avemariaghana.com', NULL, 2149, '2010-11-30 22:03:22', 'admin', 5, 1, 1, 0, NULL),
