('1291155131', 'Tsarley Korpey Beach Reasort', '1291155131.jpg', '224', 'Tsarley Korpey Beach Resort is Located 45 minutes drive away from the bustling harbour city of Tema, and 20 km off the Kasseh Junction (Ada), Tsarley Korpey Beach Resort is specifically designed and constructed to give you quality time away from the frenzied, workaday life.The very friendly and smiling in-house staff would literally swoon over you and make your stay an enjoyable one. Contact details; reservation@tsarleykorpeyresort.com 233 (0) 968 22066 , 233 (0) 20 7898660... www.tsarleykorpeyresort.com ', NULL, 1757, '2010-11-30 22:12:11', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
('1291155464', 'Our Lady of Lourdes Grotto ', '1291155464.jpg', '224', 'Our Lady of Lourdes Grotto is at Agbenoxoe some 8 minutes drive from Kpando. It serves as Tourist Center and Sacred Place for Prayers. This Statue of Our Lady of Lourdes stands some 20 feet high. The following photos are the various stations of the Cross representing what Jesus Christ went through. Observe it and share photos with interested friends.', NULL, 1836, '2010-11-30 22:17:44', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
