('1291157332', 'Rockstoneâ€™s Office', '1291157332.jpg', '213', 'After enjoying enormous success in the entertainment industry as one of the greatest rappers of all time and the forerunner of the genre â€œHipLifeâ€, Reggie now takes a new turn as the CEO of Rockstoneâ€™s Office formerly known as Office Night club. This hangout is a blend of club and pub so he terms it â€œPLUBâ€. PLUB is a self coined word from Pub and Club used by Reggie to define his new hangout in the heart of the business city of Accra. Rockstone''s Office is behind the Police Headquarters at Cantonments, Accra.', '', 1042, '2010-11-30 22:48:52', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
