('1291158115', 'Hillburi', '1291158115.jpg', '127', 'Majestically positioned in the spectacular Akwapim mountain range in the Eastern Region of Ghana, the resort is a forty five minute drive from the capital Accra and along the Aburi road. Hillburi affords breathtaking views over the evergreen valley and plains of the surrounding mountains. Contact details, Tel:  233 24-438-5008 /  233 24-426-3652 , Email: info@hillburi.com, website:www.hillburi.com', '', 1140, '2010-11-30 23:01:55', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
